## Questions Every Business Should Ask Before Signing

These ten questions expose the difference between companies that deliver and those that merely promise.

1. What specific results have you achieved for businesses in my industry?
2. Who will be doing the actual work on my account? Can I meet them?
3. What is your methodology for keyword research and content strategy?
4. How do you measure and report success? Can I see a sample report?
5. What deliverables do I own if we end the engagement?
6. How are you adapting your approach for AI search?
7. What is your average client retention rate?
8. Can I speak with 2-3 current clients as references?
9. What realistic results can I expect over 3, 6, and 12 months?
10. What do you need from me to do your best work?

